    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2) in collector-tier condition. This wide-body naturally aspirated icon features the 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant, delivering 320hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle and an advanced viscous multi-plate AWD system. The chassis is impeccably sorted, retaining its factory-spec MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension for razor-sharp turn-in. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recent rear main seal replacement. Finished in its original Arctic Silver Metallic with a flawless full-leather interior, this 4S exhibits zero bore scoring and optimal compression across all cylinders. A mechanically perfect example of the analog driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
